=Description=

"Ooooby is a collaborative commons enterprise. We reinvest all our profits into developing local food production, and ensure that all participants in the supply chain are rewarded fairly for their contribution. This includes paying our farmers 50% of the total retail value for the supply and delivery of the produce to the Ooooby hub."

